# Demo.md format

Whenever you create, update, or rebuild `Demo.md`:

- Always include **both the question and the answer** for every item
- Use a clear, study-friendly format (question, expected answer, source docs when useful)
- Never leave questions without answers
- Prefer plain language with key facts/numbers easy to scan
- Keep no-answer cases explicit (say the docs do not contain it)
